    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Heavy, durable wood from trees of the genus Magnolia, ranging in color from pale yellow to brown, used for making framing and lining of furniture, pallets, interior joinery, and boxes.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
